@startuml isp_violation
!theme plain
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

title Naruszenie ISP - "Fat Interface"

interface Worker {
  + work(): void
  + eat(): void
  + sleep(): void
  + getSalary(): double
}

class Human implements Worker {
  + work(): void
  + eat(): void
  + sleep(): void
  + getSalary(): double
}

class Robot implements Worker {
  + work(): void
  + eat(): void
  + sleep(): void
  + getSalary(): double
}

note right of Robot
  ❌ PROBLEM:
  Robot zmuszony do implementacji
  metod, których nie używa:

  public void eat() {
    throw new UnsupportedOperationException();
  }

  public void sleep() {
    throw new UnsupportedOperationException();
  }

  public double getSalary() {
    throw new UnsupportedOperationException();
  }
end note

note bottom of Worker
  ❌ "Fat Interface"
  Zbyt wiele odpowiedzialności
end note

@enduml

